{"tid":2445693,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"川普現身「拯救中國狗」活動　暗示新抱將選參議員","createTime":"2021-03-13T22:47:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T23:09:24.000Z","uid":28765,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4ce776180e47c924d48661b7c02e5fb03a311fc6","tid":2445693,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T22:47:31.000Z","msg":"美國前總統川普周五（12日）晚間驚喜現身於一場拯救中國犬隻的募款活動，並即興來了一段演講，自稱是「愛犬人士」，且在擔任總統期間多次進行過有關拯救毛孩子的會議；川普的媳婦蘿拉（Lara Trump）也在場，他在提到蘿拉時，高興地對觀眾表示「聽說她要選參議員」，頗有為媳婦拉抬之勢<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n川普到現場後才發現，次子艾瑞克（Eric Trump）的太太蘿拉也在場，原來蘿拉是募款活動的協辦人之一。近來有傳聞指蘿拉明年將競選北卡羅萊納州的參議員席位，川普對此表示，「我不知道妳要選耶」，然後又對台下觀眾高喊「我聽說她要選參議員！」台下隨即爆發出歡呼聲。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n蘿拉是土生土長的北卡州人，畢業於北卡州立大學，女兒也取名叫「卡羅萊娜」（Carolina）。她原是電視節目製作人，2016年起擔任川普競選籌劃人，替川普進行各種宣傳，對於北卡州和選舉生態可謂相當熟悉，目前尚未正式表態是否競選參議員。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210314/CSSNMYCURNG2VKLV44LBVINFA4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210314%2FCSSNMYCURNG2VKLV44LBVINFA4%2F&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfIRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=57be69d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210314%2FCSSNMYCURNG2VKLV44LBVINFA4%2F&h=986bc18b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210314/CSSNMYCURNG2VKLV44LBVINFA4/</a>"},{"pid":"022d49940b603843deb2d9d031c00e1398e7cb2c","tid":2445693,"uid":255402,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T22:51:35.000Z","msg":"侵: 中國狗比支那狗更值得拯救<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8cd5c912ba8951ce63f722ee8709fb63bdfb5b9","tid":2445693,"uid":7736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T22:56:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bpaORkXI8EA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbpaORkXI8EA&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfIRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=d61dc49d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bpaORkXI8EA</a>"},{"pid":"bd6b98cebb98bf994be1bc8431f02cc60a827c34","tid":2445693,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T22:57:49.000Z","msg":"拯救支那狗"},{"pid":"fea2055ff7aef885c6ed7062693c40b829e8d8a9","tid":2445693,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T23:09:24.000Z","msg":"侵奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}